title: Champions and finalists of UEFA EURO championship 1960 to 2016
summary: This grouped bar chart shows Number of titles/final appearances on the Y-axis for 13 different Countrys for 2 groups Winner, and Runner-up that are presented on the X-axis.

Country Spain had the maximum Number of titles/final appearances among all 2 groups, and it was for Winner. The minimum Number of titles/final appearances was observed in Country Yugoslavia for Winner.
Among all the Countrys, Runner-up had the highest Number of titles/final appearances 3.0 in Country USSR and lowest value 0.0 in Country Czechoslovakia.
There is a gap of 3.0 between the highest and lowest Number of titles/final appearances found for Runner-up in Country USSR and Czechoslovakia.
